# SSIS Customer Order Summary ETL

## Overview
This SSIS package extracts customer order data from a SQL Server stored procedure and loads it into a destination table for reporting and analysis.

## Process
- Extract data using stored procedure: sp_GetCustomersByDate
- Use parameters (StartDate, EndDate, MinOrders, Country)
- Transform data within SSIS Data Flow
- Load results into a SQL Server destination table

## Tools Used
- SQL Server
- SSIS (SQL Server Integration Services)
- Visual Studio

## Key Features
- Parameterized data extraction
- ETL pipeline design
- Data mapping and loading
- Real-world reporting scenario

